text: Norman Gagne (3 January 1911 - 28 November 1986) was a Canadian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:1986 deaths Category:Canadian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Canada Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Montreal
